    <h1>System requirements</h1><div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>This page lists the requirements that your hardware and internet connection need to fulfil if you wish to use plentymarkets.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="10">1. Required hardware, operating systems and browsers</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
